{"type": "article", "id": 30812, "title": "这本书的每一页都是一道谜题｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-09T23:01:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31304, "name": "Toasteroid"}, {"id": 31305, "name": "Blond"}, {"id": 31306, "name": "Kevin Chiam"}, {"id": 31307, "name": "Breadwood & Co."}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 221, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160809233838sgNqDh5PavAZeiku.png", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Codex Silenda by Brady Whitney &amp; Hanna Humphrey</h3><p>如果你热衷于动手解谜，这本名为 <a href=\"http://bw23brady.wix.com/portfolio#!codex-silenda-project/t9jub\" rel=\"nofollow\">Codex Silenda</a> 的解谜书会让你眼前一亮。它包含了五页不同的谜题，只有解开之后才可以翻至下一页，增强了可玩性。设计师还在书中穿插了达芬奇一位学徒的故事，其中的线索也与谜题息息相关。精妙的机械结构以及神秘的文字使它看起来就像是一件艺术品，放在桌上用作装饰也是一个不错的选择。Codex Silenda 在 Kickstarter 上线后仅用了六个小时就筹到了目标资金，制作团队会在第一批 400 本制作完成之后再开放额外的名额。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2119414279/codex-silenda-the-book-of-puzzles\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹页面</a>中的链接进行预约。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234043MKCsSpVNuBc9lgnb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234042TKAwI7yQlcCv4tHF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234044x4KwAamYJ397nzLB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234045k7gaPIHEyOGrwYmu.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080923404761MQ7wl2GUZ9oJKV.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234046rRIiko5unlU7yabT.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562592\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Toasteroid by Toasteroid</h3><p>想在吐司上煎出漂亮的图案或者是一句暖心的留言却不知道如何下手？这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.toasteroid.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Toasteroid</a> 的机器可以帮你做出一份充满趣味的吐司，它有一个配套的应用，下载后通过蓝牙向机器传输数据。只要在手机上进行简单的操作，吐司就会煎出订制的图案或者留言，颜色的深浅也可以自由控制。除此之外，你还可以选择在吐司上煎出当日的天气和温度，让本来单调的早餐时间变得更加有趣。你这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/258723592/toasteroid-first-app-controlled-smart-image-toaste\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 59 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608092340204BkdEqDxFgc5njtA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666172\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234020Mm7y4gfZ2v5WDbq9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.061041\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234023kDtvI46NOdTG7mPu.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234021vae4ECphLiXOKGoY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.069444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809234022JM2hpisNSqbKdAn1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.233824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Duo by Blond</h3><p>时尚的家电设计与无线充电技术之间的关系越发紧密，在 <a href=\"http://blond.cc/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blond</a> 工作室的总监 James Melia 看来，尽管有不少电器品牌已经推出了无线充电装置，它们的设计重心都更偏向于科技而忽略了产品与居家环境的契合。他领导的工作室最近就推出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://blond.cc/work/duo-speaker/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Duo</a> 的家电，包含一个便携式圆柱形扬声器和配套的无线充电托盘。和市面上其他同类产品不同，Blond 特意没有选择塑料制作托盘，而是使用了可丽耐人造石（Corian），这种富有触感的材质和简约的外型使 Duo 可以很好地融入室内环境当中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233957as0cvPHQAFqYGX2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233958ncdT5lEfapb6KQvA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233959DbAo0fPuJUhQyGme.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233957d4f5DAk69xnRXh80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233956BNUxA2RMgYvl8sOL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Silhouette lamp by Kevin Chiam</h3><p>初看时你很有可能觉得这个只有金属轮廓的落地灯 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41225977/Silhouette-Floor-Lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Silhouette</a> 再普通不过了。然而，只有凑近了观察你才能发现设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/kevinchiam\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kevin Chiam</a> 在 LED 灯的处理上所暗藏的“小心机”：“灯罩”底部那个被圆柱穿过的平面正是它的光源所在，另一面还可以摆放植物或是装饰品。在靠近底座的地方，Chiam 还特意设计了一个用来收纳装置，让电线不再杂乱无章。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233939GSoj6d2xlyimMPsV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233938HLziboaYtR7GqQ4w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233938ewjhk5vTbWD1m6HC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233938A7ybYVm1FfBqJIl6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233939mkTUM6vasp8cLt7o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cool Chair by Karoliina Priha &amp; Kaleb J Cardenas Z</h3><p>瑞典设计师 Karoliina Priha 与来自墨西哥的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/kalebjcardenasz\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kaleb J Cardenas Z</a> 共同设计了这把被命名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/9839527/Cool-Chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cool Chair</a> 的扶手椅，它最大的特点在于由管状靠垫交叠而成的椅背，就像是童话书中的海浪。Priha 在制作靠垫时选用了传统填充物马鬃毛，织物表面则由羊毛制成，这两种天然材料的组合保证了椅背的柔软舒适。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608092339147vlu8gPdLsX3Upjc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233914HIhB7Zw9atxSosbG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233910U63Jqw1NWRjk8fYM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608092339135UYWN0RZIJc6jo8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233914aRKVEw7exBoYlNQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233914qOUkcTXmjYnrF1bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Iron-Tek by Breadwood &amp; Co.</h3><p>蛋白粉品牌 Iron-Tek 最近委托 <a href=\"http://beardwood.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beardwood &amp; Co.</a> 重新设计了自己的 LOGO、产品包装以及网页。在主视觉上，他们在翻阅历史资料之后选择了 Harold Von Schmidt 绘制的海报，画面中的工人形象传递出自然而健康的阳刚气质。海报下方则是具有现代感的信息图，让顾客能够直观地了解到品牌的功效。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233854xuyt8rqcmaE7nfpZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466844\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233854sBhYA2RFW3SNnr5I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.283364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233854SNwUiVrkfatcmKTG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.288848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233854M8fZ3PuVLScAmOCR.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233855lp4aHXRzfTJAP0yo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}